<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">通用辅助功能</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<p class="p">The GNOME desktop includes assistive technologies to support users with
  various impairments and special needs, and to interact with common assistive
  devices. An accessibility menu can be added to the top bar, giving easier
  access to many of the accessibility features.</p>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="linkdiv "><a class="linkdiv" href="a11y-icon.html.zh-CN" title="找到辅助功能菜单"><span class="title">找到辅助功能菜单</span><span class="linkdiv-dash"> — </span><span class="desc">辅助功能菜单在顶部面板上，图标像一个小人。</span></a></div></div></div></div>
</div>
