<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">视觉障碍</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">失明</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-braille.html.zh-CN" title="使用盲文阅读屏幕">使用盲文阅读屏幕</a><span class="desc"> — 使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 屏幕阅读器和可刷新盲文显示器。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-screen-reader.html.zh-CN" title="朗读屏幕">朗读屏幕</a><span class="desc"> — 使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 屏幕阅读器朗读用户界面。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">弱视</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-mag.html.zh-CN" title="Magnify a screen area">Magnify a screen area</a><span class="desc"> — Zoom in on your screen so that it is easier to see things.</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-font-size.html.zh-CN" title="更改屏幕上的文字大小">更改屏幕上的文字大小</a><span class="desc"> — 使用较大字体使文本更易于阅读。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-cursor-blink.html.zh-CN" title="让键盘光标闪烁">让键盘光标闪烁</a><span class="desc"> — 设置插入点闪烁，以及闪烁速度。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-contrast.html.zh-CN" title="调整对比度">调整对比度</a><span class="desc"> — Make windows and buttons on the screen more (or less) vivid, so
    they’re easier to see.</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
