<div id="mobility" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">运动障碍</span></h2></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">鼠标操作</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-mousekeys.html.zh-CN" title="使用键盘来点击和移动鼠标指针">使用键盘来点击和移动鼠标指针</a><span class="desc"> — Enable mouse keys to control the mouse with the numeric
    keypad.</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-sensitivity.html.zh-CN" title="调整鼠标或触摸板的速度">调整鼠标或触摸板的速度</a><span class="desc"> — 设置鼠标或触摸板指针的移动速度。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">点击和拖动</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-right-click.html.zh-CN" title="模拟右键点击">模拟右键点击</a><span class="desc"> — 按住鼠标左键，产生右键点击。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-doubleclick.html.zh-CN" title="调整双击速度">调整双击速度</a><span class="desc"> — 控制双击时，两次点击的最小时间间隔。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-dwellclick.html.zh-CN" title="通过悬停产生点击">通过悬停产生点击</a><span class="desc"> — The <span class="gui">Hover Click</span> (Dwell Click) feature allows you to click
    by holding the mouse still.</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">键盘使用</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-repeat-keys.html.zh-CN" title="Manage repeated key presses">Manage repeated key presses</a><span class="desc"> — 设定键盘在按住一个键时不重复输入，或者设定重复的延迟时间。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-osk.html.zh-CN" title="Use an on-screen keyboard">Use an on-screen keyboard</a><span class="desc"> — Use an on-screen keyboard to enter text by clicking buttons with the
    mouse or a touchscreen.</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-bouncekeys.html.zh-CN" title="开启回弹键">开启回弹键</a><span class="desc"> — 忽略对同一个键的快速重复按键动作。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-slowkeys.html.zh-CN" title="开启慢速键">开启慢速键</a><span class="desc"> — 按键之后，屏幕显示对应字母之前，有一些延迟。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-stickykeys.html.zh-CN" title="开启粘滞键">开启粘滞键</a><span class="desc"> — 按快捷键时可以依次按下每一个键，而无需一次按住所有键。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-nav.html.zh-CN" title="键盘导航">键盘导航</a><span class="desc"> — 在没有鼠标的情况下单击和移动鼠标指针</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
